@jossshhh Dear Josh, we invite you to send us all the details of your booking and your refund request in DM so that we can assist you as best as possible. 
Thank you for your understanding. 
Have a good day, Yvonne

@AislingJane_ Dear Ais, we are sincerely sorry for the inconvenience of contacting us at this time.
We invite you to DM us with all the details of your request which will allow us to meet your expectations as well as possible  
Have a good day, Yvonne

@gideon_kure Hello Yusuf,  we sincerely apologise for the delay.
We are unable to give you a precise timeframe for refunds. We are making every effort to process all requests as quickly as possible.
Thank you for your understanding, Yvonne

@mjdickson_ Hello, we regret this incident at the arrival of your flight. Did you make your loss report online?
Once you have made your declaration online, you can follow the progress of your luggage here: https://t.co/sJeln28hmL 
Thank you, Yvonne
